\ldblquote Hurry up!\rdblquote  their mother said, and the three boys clambered onto the train. They leaned out of the window for her to kiss them good-bye, and their younger sister began to cry.\par
\ldblquote Don\rquote t, Ginny, we\rquote ll send you loads of owls.\rdblquote\par
