\ldblquote Has anyone seen a toad? Neville\rquote s lost one,\rdblquote  she said. She had a bossy sort of voice, lots of bushy brown hair, and rather large front teeth.\par
\ldblquote We\rquote ve already told him we haven\rquote t seen it,\rdblquote  said Ron, but the girl wasn\rquote t listening, she was looking at the wand in his hand.\par
\ldblquote Oh, are you doing magic? Let\rquote s see it, then.\rdblquote\par
She sat down. Ron looked taken aback.\par
\ldblquote Er \emdash  all right.\rdblquote\par
He cleared his throat.\par
\par
