\ldblquote I suppose you think you\rquote re harder to get past than a pack of en\-chantments!\rdblquote  she stormed. \ldblquote Enough of this nonsense! If I hear you\rquote ve come anywhere near here again, I\rquote ll take another fifty points from Gryffindor! Yes, Weasley, from my own House!\rdblquote\par
