\ldblquote I\rquote m sorry, Harry!\rdblquote  she wailed. \ldblquote Snape came out and asked me what I was doing, so I said I was waiting for Flitwick, and Snape went to get him, and I\rquote ve only just got away, I don\rquote t know where Snape went.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Well, that\rquote s it then, isn\rquote t it?\rdblquote  Harry said.\par
The other two stared at him. He was pale and his eyes were glit\-tering.\par
\ldblquote I\rquote m going out of here tonight and I\rquote m going to try and get to the Stone first.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote You\rquote re mad!\rdblquote  said Ron.\par
\ldblquote You can\rquote t!\rdblquote  said Hermione. \ldblquote After what McGonagall and Snape have said? You\rquote ll be expelled!\rdblquote\par
