He glared at them.\par
\ldblquote You\rquote re right, Harry,\rdblquote  said Hermione in a small voice.\par
\ldblquote I\rquote ll use the Invisibility Cloak,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote It\rquote s just lucky I got it back.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote But will it cover all three of us?\rdblquote  said Ron.\par
\ldblquote All \emdash  all three of us?\rdblquote\par
