\ldblquote But if we get caught, you two will be expelled, too.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Not if I can help it,\rdblquote  said Hermione grimly. \ldblquote Flitwick told me in secret that I got a hundred and twelve percent on his exam. They\rquote re not throwing me out after that.\rdblquote\par
